imulation study over many different scenarios, and in a case study. It is\nfound that the product and Scale Loss Score models provide more intuitive\ntreatment recommendation decisions in the majority of scenarios compared to the\nlinear and multi-linear models, and are more robust to the correlation in the\ncriteria.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 26 Jul 2021 16:14:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-27"}
