\nquicklook script for making real-time decisions during an observing run, and\ncan open a GUI displaying a minimally reduced exposure in under 15 seconds.\nDocker containers are available for ease of deploying DBSP_DRP in its quicklook\nconfiguration (without some large atmospheric model files) or in its full\nconfiguration.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 26 Jul 2021 17:22:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-29"}
