 results are new also in these\nframeworks. Moreover, the tools that we develop here have applications to\nclassical questions in Geometric Analysis on smooth, non compact Riemannian\nmanifolds with lower Ricci curvature bounds.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 26 Jul 2021 17:34:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 14 Oct 2021 07:27:15 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 16 Feb 2023 12:51:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-17"}
