y in HST/WFC3 light curves. Using\nradiative-transfer models, we obtained the different cloud layers that might be\nintroducing the spectro-photometric variability we observe for 2MASS\nJ22081363+2921215, that further support the measured enhanced variability\namplitude in the alkali lines. We provide an artistic recreation of the\nvertical cloud structure of this beta-Pictoris b analog.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 26 Jul 2021 17:59:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-13"}
