ortices. Comparing vortex encounters and\nparameters with advective wind speeds, we find evidence that high wind speeds\nat InSight may have suppressed the formation of dust devils, explaining the\nlack of imaged dust devils.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 26 Jul 2021 20:07:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 10 Sep 2021 23:23:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-14"}
