ations. Both the quantum\nand classical calculations suggest that the delocalization of preferred\npositions of the anion around the cation, which adopts different conformations\nof the ethyl chain, is on the origin of the crystallization being hampered\nduring cooling and the resulting glass-forming ability of [C2C1im][N(CN)2].\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 27 Jul 2021 03:20:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-28"}
