f Majoron are worked out\nin the model and shown to be consistent with various laboratory, astrophysical\nand cosmological constraints. The neutrino data allows sizeable couplings\nbetween the RH neutrinos and Higgsinos which can be used to probe the\npseudo-Goldstone fermion at colliders through its displaced decay vertex.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 27 Jul 2021 13:20:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 7 Oct 2021 13:54:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-08"}
